Jos Buttler scored 24 from eight balls to lead England to victory.

Jos Buttler emphasized the importance of being ultra-positive and taking advantage of the net run-rate.
Miscellaneous Highlights: England's net run-rate improved from minus 1.800 to plus 3.08.
